	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. P.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si nova queris, videbis ex his, que dominis tuis significo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus det meliora; nam singulis horis expecto nova de conflictu.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cardinales sive legati, qui ad Caesaren et regen dimissi erant a papa, pro pace, redeunt re infecta; nam Caesar petit a rege sub specie amicitię in futurum federa captiosa contra Germaniam et alios amicos, et in summa nihil est certi in illis tractatibus, per quos plus mali eveniet in republica christiana quam ex bello.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam inter cetera <persName type="auto_name">Caesar</persName> petit, ne rex comprehendat in foedere suos amicos et quod ipse eadem velit ex sua parte, ut sit post pacem liberum Caesari et regi bellum facere... iis.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vide, quorsum ista tendant.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ergo melius est pugnare.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audi reliqua: cardinalis ille, qui nuper apud vos fuit, mihi significavit <persName type="auto_name">Caesarem</persName> promittere pape, quod velit <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Angliam</placeName> ad pristinum religionis statum reducere.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ergo statim decretum est, quod cardinalis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglus</placeName> Paulus, qui <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425">Rome</placeName> est, iret ad <persName type="auto_name">Caesarem</persName> et postea ab eo in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Angliam</placeName> transiret, et brevi transiturus est.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vide et perpende diligenter artes illius Caesaris, et quam caute totum orbem bellis civilibus implicet.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Videbis brevi miseram <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Angliam</placeName> estuantem.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Marchio adhuc vivit et rursum parat arma.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De ceteris si quid habes, lubenter a te audirem.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vive, vale, vir optime.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760">Soluturo</placeName> 22a augusti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus semper Bas[safontaneus].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Decem ex camera <persName ref="p18538">Cesaris</persName> summi viri sunt inter alios in hoc conflictu rapti; hoc habui iam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viro optimo domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Bulingero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Von anderer Hand:]</note>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem herren <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Bullinger</persName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName> zu uberantwurtten zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
